text: Kalmazan () is a rural locality (a village) in Bolsheshadinsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 87 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 18 km from Mishkino, 5 km from Bolshiye Shady. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Kalmazan
